TRIPS Quiz App

Test your knowledge on the TRIPS Agreement with a 10-question quiz. You have 60 seconds per question!

Disclaimer

This project is a personal work-in-progress created for educational and exploratory purposes only. The quick questions about the TRIPS Agreement, as well as their corresponding answers and explanations, are not official nor fully validated.

Nothing in this project should be considered as authoritative or final. For accurate and up-to-date information on TRIPS, please refer to official sources such as the World Trade Organization (WTO) or academic references.
